{"tid":1417850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(理性)再係咁盲勇落去,曙光真係會消失","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T17:36:41.000Z","uid":226344,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc02ea7152751eb3940f4caac8c14a1ff5c4cd1","tid":1417850,"uid":226344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:19:22.000Z","msg":"整合一下其他post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1415821/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1415821/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1416146/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1416146/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1416569/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1416569/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1415130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1415130/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔好意思,真心希望大家唔好嫌長,睇埋佢</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地在<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">明</span></span>,佢地在<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">暗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一連串既勇武,佢地都視若無睹既時候。<br />\n<br />\n除左係佢地太無情,更多既係我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">太天真</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n運動一開始時候既勇武,令我覺得好有希望。<br />\n<br />\n但目前結果而言,其實只係我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">自high</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想打擊,分割所有兄弟,只係目前我地再做再多既勇武,只會一直出現<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">犧牲</span></span>,換唔到我地想要既結果。<br />\n<br />\n我地既最終目的係運動成功,如果大家仲拘泥係勇武兄弟既犧牲到,矛頭轉向警方,我地真係會炒<br />\n<br />\n我唔係前線果批,我知我無資格批評前線,但前線既命,已經唔單單屬於前線既自己,而係屬於<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">真.‧香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔撚想再見到勇武同手足白白送頭,我個心都好撚痛<br />\n<br />\n政府已經出左好多招,而我地KEEP住勇武既話,只會中左佢地陷阱<br />\n<br />\n希望大家反思一下Be Water,唔係只for游擊戰<br />\n<br />\n能屈能伸,行如流水係可以適用係勇武同和理非互相配合,相輔相成<br />\n<br />\n大家不要再被憤怒衝昏頭腦,我地而家有需要轉牌,先暫停硬攻。<br />\n<br />\n政府怕既係經濟,運動需要轉一轉型,先有出路"},{"pid":"935c8739d8aa6b3c5b6fbc72e41a09f1bd5d9092","tid":1417850,"uid":174578,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:19:53.000Z","msg":"唔該哂,又BLOCK一個"},{"pid":"bb77d7073b83b8bd5db2a722a47868a57b141914","tid":1417850,"uid":6742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:20:21.000Z","msg":"推！！！<br />\n<br />\n[突發！！有片！] 九龍灣連儂牆又有人撕紙！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dxkObS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dxkObS</a>"},{"pid":"92b28faa3200d17de1398fe72b74a32afd1dd848","tid":1417850,"uid":169191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:21:01.000Z","msg":"前線們，香港唔係淨係得連登。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dxienS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dxienS</a>"},{"pid":"d45ab5fb186cc68b5e29fea5db8f2dbeea2db992","tid":1417850,"uid":95541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"935c8739d8aa6b3c5b6fbc72e41a09f1bd5d9092","tid":1417850,"uid":174578,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:19:53.000Z","msg":"唔該哂,又BLOCK一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:21:27.000Z","msg":"點解要block呢？"},{"pid":"fa41490dba97a843f43d04a53e3706ae7428efc9","tid":1417850,"uid":226344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:24:04.000Z","msg":"希望大家理性,我只係加深其他post既必要,我唔介意被block"},{"pid":"ec95008f1d91c78aab8c5359b313f059af93c183","tid":1417850,"uid":226344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:27:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd34ce78db5a0ff6699bba7c6fb855affd66c8ea","tid":1417850,"uid":226344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:29:06.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"83b27f840947b158ca393f6d38390a187f837e04","tid":1417850,"uid":226344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:30:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8883e452e9da7cebec1e1448b2d6227c6d94543","tid":1417850,"uid":217415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:31:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5b1ef4c821cfb99f283a4bd0143160eca748deaa","tid":1417850,"uid":226344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:32:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"39bbc6d2620bc16701518368371c51dc3c266cbd","tid":1417850,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:32:27.000Z","msg":"再唔勇武 狗都做得 過主"},{"pid":"771c9b4963d361cb4b45c3efa486564227574e34","tid":1417850,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}